  "body": "## environment\r\n\r\nOS: Ubuntu 20.04.2 LTS\r\nnode: 14.15.4\r\nnpm: 7.5.4\r\nweb3: 1.3.2\r\nhardhat: 2.0.10\r\n\r\n## description\r\n\r\nI can't really test my dApp too much because I get disconnected after approximately 30 seconds when connecting to the node using web3.js\r\n\r\nProcess:\r\nrun `npx hardhat node` (output is ok; listens on 8545, lists the address)\r\nThen I launch my dApp which connects an instance of web3 with: `new Web3(new Web3.providers.WebsocketProvider('ws://localhost:8545'))`\r\nI subscribe to some logs\r\nI do interact with my contract and get the logs outputs in the subscribe\r\nThen I stop interacting with the chain and the dApp backend after around 30 seconds throws:\r\n\r\n```\r\n(node:117088) UnhandledPromiseRejectionWarning: Error: Maximum number of reconnect attempts reached!\r\n    at Object.MaxAttemptsReachedOnReconnectingError (/var/www/html/blockchain/beyondNFT/api/node_modules/web3-core-helpers/lib/errors.js:60:16)\r\n    at /var/www/html/blockchain/beyondNFT/api/node_modules/web3-providers-ws/lib/index.js:350:37\r\n    at Map.forEach (<anonymous>)\r\n    at WebsocketProvider.reconnect (/var/www/html/blockchain/beyondNFT/api/node_modules/web3-providers-ws/lib/index.js:349:27)\r\n    at WebsocketProvider._onClose (/var/www/html/blockchain/beyondNFT/api/node_modules/web3-providers-ws/lib/index.js:149:14)\r\n    at W3CWebSocket._dispatchEvent [as dispatchEvent] (/var/www/html/blockchain/beyondNFT/api/node_modules/yaeti/lib/EventTarget.js:115:12)\r\n    at W3CWebSocket.onConnectFailed (/var/www/html/blockchain/beyondNFT/api/node_modules/websocket/lib/W3CWebSocket.js:219:14)\r\n    at WebSocketClient.<anonymous> (/var/www/html/blockchain/beyondNFT/api/node_modules/websocket/lib/W3CWebSocket.js:59:25)\r\n    at WebSocketClient.emit (events.js:315:20)\r\n    at WebSocketClient.failHandshake (/var/www/html/blockchain/beyondNFT/api/node_modules/websocket/lib/WebSocketClient.js:339:10)\r\n    at ClientRequest.<anonymous> (/var/www/html/blockchain/beyondNFT/api/node_modules/websocket/lib/WebSocketClient.js:278:18)\r\n    at ClientRequest.emit (events.js:315:20)\r\n    at HTTPParser.parserOnIncomingClient (_http_client.js:641:27)\r\n    at HTTPParser.parserOnHeadersComplete (_http_common.js:126:17)\r\n    at Socket.socketOnData (_http_client.js:509:22)\r\n    at Socket.emit (events.js:315:20)\r\n```\r\n",
